<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2001—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/107/14">Pub. L. 107–14</ref> substituted “hereinafter” for “hereafter”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1998—<ref href="/us/pl/105/368">Pub. L. 105–368</ref> substituted “Native American Veteran Housing Loan Program Account” for “Housing loan program account” in section catchline.</p>
